snippet.title: Time For A New World | EVERYWHERE Official Reveal Trailer 2023
snippet.description:
This is EVERYWHERE! 💜 Watch the first gameplay footage. 
Create a free account and apply to the Closed Alpha Test: https://go.everywhere.game/playalpha
EVERYWHERE is community-driven gaming, a place where you can unleash your imagination to build, play, and connect.

Follow us on: 
TW: https://twitter.com/everywheregame 
IG: https://www.instagram.com/everywheregame
FB: https://www.facebook.com/everywhere.game
TT: https://www.tiktok.com/@everywhere 

And join the conversation: 
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/EverywhereGame/ 
Discord: https://discord.gg/EverywhereGame 

#EVERYWHEREgame #TFANW
